  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1057">
<l>ikaḻnteḷḷā tīvāraik kāṇiṉ makiḻntuḷḷa</l>
<l>muḷḷu ḷuvappa tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Beggars rejoice exceedingly when they behold those who bestow (their alms) with kindness and courtesy.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
